{
  "stem": "15686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We went to services Friday night and Saturday morning, if my father didn't have to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He made sure that I went and my brother went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We both-- my brother and I-- sang in the synagogue choir.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Usually synagogues had boys choirs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We celebrated all the holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My father never worked on the holidays.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- without keeping a kosher home, yet we observed all the traditions, OK?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think this comes as close to conservatism or more modern orthodoxy in this country as you could in those days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was never any problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, when I was a little boy, it was just traditional at Friday nights and Saturday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would have a Friday night dinner, and my mother would prepare it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had at Passover, we changed dishes and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father would conduct a Seder, and many relatives would be invited.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a very rich, full Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What did you-- tell me about schools you went to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since I was born in 1925, I started school in 1931 or so, when I was about six years old.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, there was really no problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It so happened that the best school in the neighborhood where we lived, in terms of academic work and also the most convenient, was a Catholic elementary school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, Catholic elementary schools were supported by the Catholic Diocese of Berlin, but they were not, as in this country, taught by nuns or brothers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were lay teachers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And basically they had the same curriculum as the city schools, with the exception that after regular classes, there was a class in catechism.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Jewish kids in the school, and there were a dozen or so, were excused from that.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
